42:10.544 --> 42:12.511
Well, the good news is that
I don't have an STD,

42:12.513 --> 42:14.082
which means
you don't either.

42:18.652 --> 42:21.420
You never did.

42:21.422 --> 42:22.657
Oh, my...

42:39.339 --> 42:40.475
- Ooh!
- Oh!

42:47.547 --> 42:49.147
I don't know.

42:49.149 --> 42:51.018
Someone said two guys
and their girlfriends.

43:20.681 --> 43:22.880
Bartender, I think we need
a couple drinks over here.

43:22.882 --> 43:25.583
Oh, come on,
come on, come on.

43:33.426 --> 43:35.659
Come on!

43:40.901 --> 43:42.136
Yes.

43:49.343 --> 43:50.377
It's all good.

44:58.946 --> 45:00.478
Big meeting today.

45:00.480 --> 45:01.745
We're gonna finalize plans
for the church,

45:01.747 --> 45:03.547
- so wish me luck.
- Good luck, honey.

45:03.549 --> 45:06.384
But... food?

45:06.386 --> 45:07.919
- Off to school.
- I love you, honey.

45:07.921 --> 45:10.355
Food? Breakfast?

45:10.357 --> 45:11.726
- Love you.
- Have a good day.

45:23.536 --> 45:26.437
Oh, my God.

45:30.944 --> 45:32.647
Oh, no.

45:33.614 --> 45:35.879
This can't be happening.

45:35.881 --> 45:38.650
What is this?

45:46.660 --> 45:48.196
Oh, my God.

45:53.700 --> 45:55.636
Robert.

45:57.904 --> 45:59.404
We are down to the wire,

45:59.406 --> 46:01.473
so whatever it is,
it can wait.

46:01.475 --> 46:02.973
Actually...

46:02.975 --> 46:04.211
this can't.

46:18.725 --> 46:20.025
Has Mr. Getz called?

46:20.027 --> 46:21.592
Not yet.

46:21.594 --> 46:23.560
But the potential clients
that we lined up

46:23.562 --> 46:24.862
because of the church job,

46:24.864 --> 46:26.730
they all cancelled
their appointments.

46:26.732 --> 46:28.400
Every one.

46:28.402 --> 46:30.634
I told them that someone
is trying to hurt you.

46:30.636 --> 46:31.935
I know this can't be true.

46:31.937 --> 46:33.404
Of course it's not.

46:33.406 --> 46:36.507
This is somebody's idea
of a sick joke.

46:36.509 --> 46:38.710
Who's seen this?

46:38.712 --> 46:41.449
Um...
Everyone.

46:42.582 --> 46:44.848
Tell 'em to
get back to work.

46:44.850 --> 46:45.885
Okay.

46:58.765 --> 47:00.931
Isabelle!

47:10.710 --> 47:14.511
My whole life is destroyed.

47:14.513 --> 47:15.679
Your life?

47:17.017 --> 47:19.817
All of my patients
cancelled their appointments.

47:19.819 --> 47:21.419
How am I gonna pay rent?

47:21.421 --> 47:23.687
I'm gonna lose everything.

47:23.689 --> 47:26.293
I thought you're the one
that posted that list.

47:27.694 --> 47:29.694
Why would I have
posted that list?

47:29.696 --> 47:31.895
My name was on it.

47:31.897 --> 47:34.998
That's my private life.
I don't just share that with anybody.

47:35.000 --> 47:38.902
This can't be happening.
Oh, my God.

47:38.904 --> 47:40.807
Somebody is out to ruin us.

47:44.477 --> 47:46.844
Oh, my God.

47:46.846 --> 47:49.582
Do Abbey and Robert know?

47:50.984 --> 47:52.817
When they left this morning,
they didn't know,

47:52.819 --> 47:54.085
but I'm sure
they know by now.

47:54.087 --> 47:55.853
I'm sure everybody knows.

47:55.855 --> 47:58.823
It's... It's out there.

47:58.825 --> 48:00.658
We're gonna be okay.

48:00.660 --> 48:02.627
And you know why?

48:02.629 --> 48:04.565
Because we have each other.

48:05.698 --> 48:07.165
Okay?

48:07.167 --> 48:08.469
Okay.

48:17.643 --> 48:19.009
It's a sad day
for all of us.

48:19.011 --> 48:21.011
Look, Mr. Getz,
I can assure you,

48:21.013 --> 48:22.980
there's been some sort of
terrible mistake.

48:22.982 --> 48:24.815
- I'll say.
- Look, my wife and I,

48:24.817 --> 48:26.618
all we did is
is we went dancing there.

48:26.620 --> 48:28.853
Somebody clearly edited that
video to make her look that way.

48:28.855 --> 48:31.022
We had such high hopes
when we came to you.

48:31.024 --> 48:32.656
We were sure you were
the right man for the job.

48:32.658 --> 48:34.759
I am.

48:34.761 --> 48:37.562
No, we can't be in business with
people that don't share our values.

48:37.564 --> 48:39.196
Look, Mr. Getz, come on.

48:39.198 --> 48:42.833
We... We've been working on
the blueprints for weeks now.

48:42.835 --> 48:46.136
We are ready to make you
the most beautiful church.

48:46.138 --> 48:48.839
And you expect my congregation
to flock to a house of God

48:48.841 --> 48:50.074
that's been built by a man

48:50.076 --> 48:53.444
whose wife has sex
with other men?

48:53.446 --> 48:55.879
On camera.

48:55.881 --> 48:58.482
I had so many plans for us.
What a disappointment.

48:58.484 --> 49:01.986
Look, I... I'm no expert
on the Bible,

49:01.988 --> 49:03.924
but I know that it
talks about forgiveness.

49:07.560 --> 49:09.963
Do not quote scripture
to me, son.

49:25.779 --> 49:28.179
I can't go back to school.

49:28.181 --> 49:30.781
They'll just laugh at me
'til graduation day.

49:30.783 --> 49:33.150
Oh, look, it's Abbey.
You know what her mom is.

49:33.152 --> 49:35.553
No doubt she'll follow
in her footsteps.

49:35.555 --> 49:38.823
Abbey, honey,
it's not what it seems.

49:38.825 --> 49:41.692
Really? 'Cause from the videos
everyone's seen,

49:41.694 --> 49:44.761
it's pretty clear it's
exactly what it seems.

49:44.763 --> 49:47.866
Abbey, I don't remember
any of it.

49:47.868 --> 49:50.734
I swear. It's like I was
drugged or something.

49:50.736 --> 49:53.740
I don't know, but your mom would
never do something like that.

49:54.841 --> 49:56.176
But you did.

50:01.181 --> 50:02.883
People make mistakes.

50:06.252 --> 50:09.254
Joey broke up with me today
because of your mistakes.

50:09.256 --> 50:11.154
I'm sorry.

50:11.156 --> 50:13.993
What do I have now,
a mom who's a perv?

50:15.227 --> 50:17.694
What would you have said
if I had done it?

50:17.696 --> 50:19.531
I'm sorry.

50:19.533 --> 50:21.000
Don't touch me.

50:29.910 --> 50:31.708
Oh, my God.

50:56.169 --> 50:57.234
Where are you going?

50:57.236 --> 50:59.837
Why do you care?

50:59.839 --> 51:01.542
Don't talk to me
like that.

51:06.078 --> 51:07.911
I'll be at Stacy's.

51:07.913 --> 51:11.281
She said I could stay there
'til this all blows over.

51:11.283 --> 51:13.620
Who knows how long
that'll take.

51:30.837 --> 51:32.540
I saw the video.

51:34.040 --> 51:35.942
Babe, I'm sorry.

51:37.076 --> 51:39.042
How many guys were there
that night?

51:39.044 --> 51:40.280
I don't remember.

51:43.616 --> 51:45.817
I just remember getting there,

51:45.819 --> 51:47.685
and then waking up
in Isabelle's car.

51:47.687 --> 51:50.190
That's all I remember,
I swear.

51:56.363 --> 51:58.332
I guess that explains
the STD test.

52:01.835 --> 52:03.234
Here's the thing, Bob,

52:03.236 --> 52:05.902
you do have rights when
a club claims to be private,

52:05.904 --> 52:09.339
but you have to prove who's
responsible for leaking the names.

52:09.341 --> 52:11.808
You're kidding.
I have to prove it?

52:11.810 --> 52:13.176
What am I,
Sherlock Holmes?

52:13.178 --> 52:16.013
Well, kinda, unless evidence
falls from the sky,

52:16.015 --> 52:20.350
you have basically no
legal recourse whatsoever.

52:20.352 --> 52:22.053
Well, then I guess it's
gonna be a piece of cake

52:22.055 --> 52:24.721
you helping me with
what I need now.

52:24.723 --> 52:25.922
I want a trial separation.

52:25.924 --> 52:28.091
Oh, no,
that's a bad idea.

52:28.093 --> 52:29.661
Once you get to that point,

52:29.663 --> 52:32.163
it almost always leads
to divorce.

52:32.165 --> 52:34.966
And as your lawyer,
and as your best friend,

52:34.968 --> 52:36.299
I don't think you want that.

52:36.301 --> 52:40.705
I can't be in
the same house with her, Ben.

52:40.707 --> 52:42.272
Not while this is going on.

52:42.274 --> 52:43.741
I need to get out.

52:43.743 --> 52:45.743
All right.

52:45.745 --> 52:47.277
If you really decide
to go through with it,

52:47.279 --> 52:50.781
I have a small place
you can rent in town.

52:50.783 --> 52:53.283
It's been vacant a few months.

52:53.285 --> 52:55.353
I was actually
about to place an ad.

52:55.355 --> 52:57.321
Well, don't.

52:57.323 --> 52:58.388
I'll take it.

52:58.390 --> 53:00.093
Okay.

53:01.093 --> 53:02.960
Thanks, Ben.

53:02.962 --> 53:06.063
So,
as you can see,

53:06.065 --> 53:07.699
I have no other choice.

53:07.701 --> 53:10.033
Please. Someone is
trying to ruin me,

53:10.035 --> 53:12.002
my life, my career,
everything.

53:12.004 --> 53:13.471
I feel for you, I do,

53:13.473 --> 53:16.908
but my first priority
is the children.

53:16.910 --> 53:20.444
As is mine.
I love those kids.

53:20.446 --> 53:22.980
Please, I would never do
anything to hurt them.

53:22.982 --> 53:25.049
I am sorry, Morgan.

53:25.051 --> 53:26.317
Please,
just let me continue.

53:26.319 --> 53:28.118
I can't.
I can't.

53:28.120 --> 53:30.987
It's against policy.

53:30.989 --> 53:33.156
You need to leave.

53:33.158 --> 53:34.193
At least for now.

53:37.196 --> 53:38.765
I need your ID.

53:47.506 --> 53:48.908
I am sorry.

54:16.902 --> 54:18.435
We have to
sell the cars,

54:18.437 --> 54:20.837
we have to get rid of
the country club memberships,

54:20.839 --> 54:22.776
and we have to sell
the vacation home.

54:24.210 --> 54:25.245
Everything?

54:28.915 --> 54:31.915
Yeah, that's what happens
when you declare bankruptcy.

54:31.917 --> 54:33.120
Everything goes.

54:35.321 --> 54:37.855
And I'd keep my distance from
you little play pal there.

54:37.857 --> 54:40.290
I'm pretty sure that Isabelle
had something to do with this.

54:40.292 --> 54:42.460
No.

54:42.462 --> 54:44.362
Her name was
on the list, too.

54:44.364 --> 54:45.996
She's gonna lose
her business.

54:45.998 --> 54:47.397
She's suffering
just like we are.

54:47.399 --> 54:49.102
I doubt it.

54:52.437 --> 54:55.239
I'm sleeping
downstairs tonight.

54:55.241 --> 54:57.507
Babe, don't do that.

54:59.578 --> 55:01.281
Babe, please.

56:07.647 --> 56:10.882
<i>Hey, it's Abbey.
Leave a message.</i>

56:10.884 --> 56:12.350
Hey, Abbey, it's Dad.

56:12.352 --> 56:15.353
Would you please call me back
when you get this?

56:15.355 --> 56:17.087
Thank you.

56:29.201 --> 56:30.467
Dad called.

56:30.469 --> 56:34.006
He gave me the key
to his new place.

56:35.375 --> 56:39.379
Mom, I'm sorry.

56:41.413 --> 56:43.380
Honey, I'm sorry.

56:43.382 --> 56:45.085
None of this is your fault.

56:55.127 --> 56:58.395
I need your help
staging the house, okay?

56:58.397 --> 56:59.663
Okay.

56:59.665 --> 57:01.399
We have no idea
who did it.

57:01.401 --> 57:03.433
Yeah, well, somebody from
this club uploaded that list.

57:03.435 --> 57:06.103
A disgruntled employee.

57:06.105 --> 57:08.406
A drunk customer.
Somebody's ex.

57:08.408 --> 57:11.275
Look, buddy, I've lost 30
percent of my clientele already.

57:11.277 --> 57:12.643
They're asking me
for refunds.

57:12.645 --> 57:14.245
I've got a truck load of
lawsuits coming at me.

57:14.247 --> 57:15.612
Can you blame them?

57:15.614 --> 57:18.949
The list was supposed to be
confidential.

57:18.951 --> 57:20.317
Are you listening to
anything I'm saying?

57:20.319 --> 57:22.152
I'm losing my shirt here.

57:22.154 --> 57:25.091
If I knew who it was,
I'd be singing like Aretha Franklin!

57:26.993 --> 57:29.025
Well, you have to have
some sort of idea.

57:31.230 --> 57:33.297
Look, you look like
a smart guy.

57:33.299 --> 57:35.369
You think you could
fix this mess?

57:36.502 --> 57:37.734
I just might be able to.

57:40.105 --> 57:42.573
- Hey.
- Hi.

57:42.575 --> 57:43.975
I just wanted to
check on you.

57:43.977 --> 57:45.509
I left you
a couple of messages,

57:45.511 --> 57:46.978
and I haven't heard back so...

57:46.980 --> 57:48.279
Please, come in.

57:48.281 --> 57:49.315
Thanks.

57:51.250 --> 57:52.449
I didn't have my phone
on me all day

57:52.451 --> 57:54.185
because we had
an open house today.

57:54.187 --> 57:56.520
Looks like we sold the house.

57:56.522 --> 57:57.658
Wow.

57:58.591 --> 58:00.127
- Hey.
- Hey!

58:01.694 --> 58:04.328
So, I'm about to make dinner.
You want to join us?

58:04.330 --> 58:06.364
Um, I... I'd love to.
Thank you.

58:06.366 --> 58:08.065
Okay, why don't you guys
hang out,

58:08.067 --> 58:09.333
and I'll let you know
when dinner's ready.

58:09.335 --> 58:10.701
Okay.

58:10.703 --> 58:12.536
She's going through
such a hard time.

58:12.538 --> 58:14.705
Thanks so much for
being there for her.

58:14.707 --> 58:17.507
Of course.

58:17.509 --> 58:20.046
Trust me,
it's my pleasure.

58:21.180 --> 58:23.250
He was such a sweet guy.

58:25.051 --> 58:26.683
Your boyfriend?

58:26.685 --> 58:29.252
Ex because,
you know...

58:29.254 --> 58:31.087
the video.

58:31.089 --> 58:33.690
Oh, honey, I'm sorry.

58:33.692 --> 58:36.330
You'll find someone new,
I promise.

58:37.263 --> 58:39.129
I don't know.

58:39.131 --> 58:41.031
I'm not like you.

58:41.033 --> 58:43.500
You know, beautiful.

58:43.502 --> 58:45.205
Thank you, Abbey.

58:46.538 --> 58:48.607
But I didn't always
look like this.

58:51.810 --> 58:56.513
People used to call me
fat and ugly and...

58:56.515 --> 58:59.549
it got so bad
that I, um...

58:59.551 --> 59:02.386
thought about
killing myself.

59:02.388 --> 59:03.654
My gosh.

59:03.656 --> 59:06.524
But...

59:06.526 --> 59:10.527
then I met someone
and things turned around.

59:10.529 --> 59:12.763
So I promise you...

59:12.765 --> 59:15.366
you'll meet someone new.

59:15.368 --> 59:16.636
I mean,
you're beautiful.

59:18.404 --> 59:20.370
Yes, you are.

59:20.372 --> 59:22.605
You just don't realize it.

59:22.607 --> 59:26.509
Look, it just so happens
that I have

59:26.511 --> 59:29.413
my fantastic
bag of tricks.

59:29.415 --> 59:31.649
How about I show you?

59:31.651 --> 59:33.451
Come on.

59:45.297 --> 59:47.765
How's it going, ladies?

59:47.767 --> 59:49.632
We'll be right down.

59:49.634 --> 59:51.470
Okay,
dinner's being served.

59:54.107 --> 59:56.777
Hold on, hold on, hold on,
we're almost there.

59:58.444 --> 59:59.676
Okay.

59:59.678 --> 01:00:01.312
All right.

01:00:01.314 --> 01:00:02.582
You can turn around.

01:00:04.817 --> 01:00:06.219
Wow.

01:00:08.453 --> 01:00:11.522
Now every boy will be lining
up to talk to you at school.

01:00:11.524 --> 01:00:13.190
Thank you.

01:00:13.192 --> 01:00:15.592
Totally welcome.

01:00:15.594 --> 01:00:16.830
Okay, now let me finish.

01:00:21.134 --> 01:00:22.732
Can I tell you a secret?

01:00:22.734 --> 01:00:25.469
Of course.

01:00:25.471 --> 01:00:27.407
I've never been to
a club before.

01:00:28.640 --> 01:00:31.609
My mom won't let me go.

01:00:31.611 --> 01:00:33.409
You're kidding me,
right?

01:00:33.411 --> 01:00:34.777
No.

01:00:34.779 --> 01:00:36.547
I'm one of those nerds.

01:00:36.549 --> 01:00:39.783
You know, straight A's,
don't smoke, don't drink,

01:00:39.785 --> 01:00:41.618
still a virgin.

01:00:41.620 --> 01:00:43.689
My mom's really big
on abstinence.

01:00:45.591 --> 01:00:48.324
Or was.

01:00:48.326 --> 01:00:52.228
Look, those are all
really great things.

01:00:52.230 --> 01:00:54.230
But sometimes a girl's
just gotta dance, right?

01:00:59.672 --> 01:01:02.142
Do you think anyone would
want to dance with me?

01:01:05.911 --> 01:01:07.547
Absolutely.

01:01:09.681 --> 01:01:10.716
Mom.

01:01:19.524 --> 01:01:20.824
What do you think?

01:01:20.826 --> 01:01:21.859
Isabelle did it.

01:01:21.861 --> 01:01:23.661
Isn't she pretty?

01:01:23.663 --> 01:01:25.862
Is this some kind of
a joke, Isabelle?

01:01:25.864 --> 01:01:28.498
No, we just thought that,
you know...

01:01:28.500 --> 01:01:29.766
Mom, we thought that
the three of us

01:01:29.768 --> 01:01:31.868
could go out
after dinner and...

01:01:31.870 --> 01:01:34.638
and it would be like
a new life sort of thing.

01:01:34.640 --> 01:01:36.373
Why don't you like it?

01:01:36.375 --> 01:01:39.409
You're too young to be
dressed like this, Abbey.

01:01:39.411 --> 01:01:40.944
You have no idea
what's going on.

01:01:40.946 --> 01:01:43.813
Okay, I was just trying to
get her to express herself.

01:01:43.815 --> 01:01:45.748
Oh, so now you're criticizing
the way I raise my daughter?

01:01:45.750 --> 01:01:47.283
Mom!

01:01:47.285 --> 01:01:48.551
Okay, you know what?
It's all right.

01:01:48.553 --> 01:01:49.953
We'll do it
another night. Okay?

01:01:49.955 --> 01:01:51.355
I should probably go.

01:01:51.357 --> 01:01:52.589
Yeah, you should.

01:01:52.591 --> 01:01:53.924
And there isn't gonna be
another night.

01:01:53.926 --> 01:01:55.993
Gosh, Mom, you never
let me do anything!

01:01:55.995 --> 01:01:58.828
Go upstairs, wash your face,
put your pajamas on.

01:01:58.830 --> 01:02:00.700
And what if I don't?!

01:02:02.935 --> 01:02:05.572
Abbey! Not tonight!

01:02:47.946 --> 01:02:49.612
I know that she's
going through a hard time,

01:02:49.614 --> 01:02:50.913
but she doesn't have to

01:02:50.915 --> 01:02:52.716
treat me like
I'm five years old.

01:02:52.718 --> 01:02:55.486
Abbey,
your mom loves you.

01:02:55.488 --> 01:02:56.853
Really?

01:02:56.855 --> 01:02:58.959
She's got a pretty
messed up way of showing it.

01:03:01.660 --> 01:03:03.426
Did your mom
treat you like this?

01:03:03.428 --> 01:03:05.596
I don't know my mom.

01:03:05.598 --> 01:03:07.998
Never met my dad.

01:03:08.000 --> 01:03:09.500
I was a foster kid.

01:03:09.502 --> 01:03:11.969
Oh...

01:03:11.971 --> 01:03:13.974
I'm so sorry.
I didn't know.

01:03:16.808 --> 01:03:18.509
You have no idea
how lucky you are

01:03:18.511 --> 01:03:20.680
that you have parents
who love you.

01:03:21.946 --> 01:03:24.517
You're right.
I know you're right.

01:03:26.785 --> 01:03:29.588
I don't love her,
I do not want her.

01:03:30.556 --> 01:03:32.823
Okay. My turn.

01:03:32.825 --> 01:03:33.857
Can I tell you a secret?

01:03:33.859 --> 01:03:35.625
Of course.

01:03:35.627 --> 01:03:39.698
I would trade places with you
in a heartbeat.

01:03:42.368 --> 01:03:44.967
Okay, enough about that.

01:03:44.969 --> 01:03:46.969
Let's go party.

01:03:46.971 --> 01:03:48.672
Wooo!

01:03:48.674 --> 01:03:51.375
Woo-woo!

01:03:58.884 --> 01:04:00.116
How old are you?

01:04:00.118 --> 01:04:03.353
Oh, honey, she's fine.

01:04:03.355 --> 01:04:05.455
Here's her ID.

