01:08:26.919 --> 01:08:29.285
Just meet me in person.

01:08:29.287 --> 01:08:30.589
Okay? Let me explain.

01:08:31.857 --> 01:08:33.689
Meet me at my place,
30 minutes.

01:08:33.692 --> 01:08:35.595
Fifth and Riviera.

01:08:40.232 --> 01:08:41.798
